<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Simple Performance Test</title>
  <style>
    /* Only essential inline styles */
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; }
    .hero { background: white; padding: 4rem 0; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1rem; }
    .flex { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .flex { flex-direction: row; } }
    .content { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { 
      .content { width: 50%; padding-right: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0; }
      .image-container { width: 50%; position: relative; }
    }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .image-wrapper { position: relative; margin-top: -384px; display: block; }
    img { max-width: 90%; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .card { position: absolute; bottom: -84px; right: -10px; background: #ebf5ff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); max-width: 300px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="flex">
        <div class="content">
          <h1>Transform Your Digital Presence: Human Powered Digital Solutions, Accelerated With AI</h1>
          <p>We've ranked #1, #2, and #3 for our main niche in just ONE week using our proven AI optimization techniques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <!-- Direct HTML image with explicit width/height, no Astro Image -->
            <img 
              src="/digital-visibility-square-mobile.webp"
              width="400"
              height="400"
              alt="Digital Visibility"
              loading="eager"
              fetchpriority="high"
              decoding="sync"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; margin-bottom:0.5rem; color:#2563eb;">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" style="margin-right:0.5rem;">
