              </svg>
              <span style="font-weight:600;">Proven Results</span>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; color:#1d4ed8; margin:0.5rem 0;">Top 3 Rankings</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:#4b5563; margin:0;">in just 1 week</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
